<div style=\"height:39px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-flip-ef5551e3\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-flip anim flipY has-light-back-bg has-dark-front-bg\"><div class=\"o-flip-inner\"><div class=\"o-flip-front\"><div class=\"o-flip-content\"><h3>Building Custom AI Agents<\/h3><p><\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"o-flip-back\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn to design, build, and deploy custom AI agents tailored to your specific departmental or research needs.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Want us to develop courses for your institution? <\/strong><br>We can build bespoke courses personalised to your organisation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-212821f5 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-secondary\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/book-a-call\/\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">Book a Call<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline is-style-primary is-style-outline--3\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/worksmart-ai.co.uk\/contact-us\/\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">Email Us<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-nv-site-bg-color has-neve-link-color-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-982d9ef0d66bd96c5ea62631cc0af01e\" style=\"padding-top:64px;padding-bottom:64px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2db22277 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-nv-site-bg-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-0bdece374e075c5bed4efc07ca8b6658\"><em><em>\u201cOn average, people say AI has made them 33% more productive and saves them about 1.3 hours per day.\u201d<\/em><\/em><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right has-nv-site-bg-color has-text-color\">&#8211; <em><em>AI Collaboration Index 2025, Atlassian.<\/em><\/em><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-nv-light-bg-background-color has-background\" style=\"padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:20px\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-0ec7d70e wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:32px\"><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">How we help you succeed<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">A structured, people-first approach to confident and measurable AI adoption.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-31f199e8\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline\"><div class=\"o-timeline-root\">\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item-7cd70e76\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item\"><div class=\"o-timeline-container\"><div class=\"o-timeline-icon\"><i class=\"fas fa-circle\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"o-timeline-content\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left\">Free Initial Consultation<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A collaborative discussion to understand your institution&#8217;s goals and challenges and see where you are on your AI journey.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item-dbd3db82\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item\"><div class=\"o-timeline-container\"><div class=\"o-timeline-icon\"><i class=\"fas fa-circle\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"o-timeline-content\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">AI Literacy &amp; Needs Analysis<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A collaborative discussion to understand your institution&#8217;s goals and challenges and see where you are on your AI journey.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item-50a46df6\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item\"><div class=\"o-timeline-container\"><div class=\"o-timeline-icon\"><i class=\"fas fa-circle\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"o-timeline-content\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Personalised Workshops<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Choose four of our workshops for us to personalise and deliver. Expert-led, hands-on training sessions (F2F or online) tailored to your institution.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item-ea4c7822\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item\"><div class=\"o-timeline-container\"><div class=\"o-timeline-icon\"><i class=\"fas fa-circle\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"o-timeline-content\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">On-Demand Online Courses<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On-demand access to asynchronous courses that reinforce and extend the learning from our live workshops, for up to 100 staff per package.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item-9f159293\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item\"><div class=\"o-timeline-container\"><div class=\"o-timeline-icon\"><i class=\"fas fa-circle\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"o-timeline-content\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Strategic Roadmap Session<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A high-level session with your leadership to translate training insights into a clear action plan for sustaining momentum.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item-9d64fa8f\" class=\"wp-block-themeisle-blocks-timeline-item\"><div class=\"o-timeline-container\"><div class=\"o-timeline-icon\"><i class=\"fas fa-circle\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"o-timeline-content\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ongoing Support<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Continuous access to resources and our &#8220;AI Cafe&#8221; drop-in sessions to keep momentum strong as AI evolves. Follow up calls with SLT.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n